-Download Retropie for Rpi3
-Unzip
-Flash to micro SD
-plug in to pi, plug into screen
-Install packages on retropie from internet connection using either wifi or ethernet

Get flash drive formatted to NTFS or FAT
Create empty folder in home folder labeled 'retropie'
Plug USB into pi, wait 30 seconds, unplug
Add ROMS and BIOS files to correct corresponding folders
Plug back in, wait for 30 more seconds, unplug
Restart Senexito
Play, enjoy :D



GBA
